Release 1, MVP:

  - Usefully view your own profile
  - Redirect to "enter questions" at sensible times
  - Calculate basic match based on questions
  - Inform user of matching jobs at some reasonable times

Testing Before Release 1:

  - Make sure company questions and perfect company questions can be
    answered correctly and the correct values written to the DB

Monitoring:
  - Daily RSS feed of vital info like total users, logins & questions, etc.
  - App console with the same info, and exceptions

Auditing:
  - vestal_versions, notes on why a modification happened

Testing/Prototyping:

  - Add toggle to show or not show demo profiles for matches
  - Enter a bunch of demo profiles for matches

Important, but probably not release 1:

  - Cucumber tests

Usability:

  - When entering jobs, set start_date on following row to end_date just
    entered, unless that date has been changed manually at some point

Formatting and Prettiness:

  - Custom 404 page
  - Pretty up various devise and registration views
  - Add an "about" link
  - Add a "privacy" link
